eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has the details. #eNCA #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Arise and Shine Gospel Church leader claims he was tortured by police into admitting that he sexually assaulted dozens of young men at his church. Benjamin Dingiso (52) was applying for bail at the Palm Ridge Magistrates Court in Ekurhuleni. He now faces 13 charges, including rape and sexual assault after the state added more charges. eNCA's Manqoba Mchunu has the details in the video above .